                        <h3 class="heading">Madeira Adoption Community</h3>
                        <p>Madeira Adoption Community is a place where all animal rescuers can put animals up for adoption. From young kittens to long-term shelter animals; all creatures who are looking for a loving home can be found here and easily adopted. There is no need to go to several places to see what animals are available; they are right here for you to fall in love with!</p>
