                        <span class="flaticon-dog-eating"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h3 class="heading">How does it work?</h3>
                        <p>As a user you can brows all adoptable animals. You can search by type of animal, area, age, breed; whatever you want. When you find your new furry soulmate, you can log in and apply to adopt your future cat, dog, hamster, ferret or whatever other animal you want to give a loving home to. Your application will be sent to the shelter, association, foster family or other organisation, who will then judge your application.</p>
                        <p>As a shelter or other animal rescuer you can create an account and upload photos and details such as name, age, medical status, and of course the animals personality. You can also upload Terms of Responsibility or Adoption Agreements for future adopters to sign. This will save time, paperwork and in the end, animals lives!</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-custom d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"><span class="fa fa-chevron-right"></span><i class="sr-only">Read more</i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
