                        <span class="flaticon-grooming"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h3 class="heading">Why adopt?</h3>
                        <p>Madeira has many animals who have a rough start in life, who are living on the street or have been abandoned at a later age. You can make the difference between a life on the streets and a loving home. What do you get when you adopt an animal? You will get a friend for life who will love you in a way only an animal can. And you saved a life!</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-custom d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"><span class="fa fa-chevron-right"></span><i class="sr-only">Read more</i></a>
